<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وفيها سار أتابك نحو بغداد <span class="c2">(٨)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وفتح بُرْسُق حماه) <span class="c2">(٩)</span> <span class="c2">(١٠)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
